{
  "stem": "3341.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had the very first-hand connections to these very influential people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through these connections, we were able to find out-- maybe one month ahead-- we will be nationalized.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we arranged, again through these connections, then who should be the-- the trustee.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we knew from the beginning, through the back door, that there will be two women named in trustee of our firm.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, we put there one woman, who was working for us for many years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She came as a junior girl, she worked up to a leading position in the retail shop, so we pressed, and also with help of money, we arranged with the Minister of Commerce. that one-- this lady who will be our trustee should be so and so.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was-- by the way, I have to disclose it, she was a girlfriend-- secret girlfriend-- of my brother, who was the manager-- still official manager of the firm.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The other woman, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We knew we will have to have two.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was a precaution of the new fascist government.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When there are two strange women, one will watch the other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They will-- they both governed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They both steered quite nicely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But that was the safety [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when we-- when we found out the other woman will be a strange person, so we arranged somehow-- no, we heard.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We heard, actually, before she came to the shop, she was named.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she was the wife of a [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] that was the local Slovakian equal to the SS, but the Slovakian part.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because Slovakia had a proper army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The second army was the Slovakian Guard, and above them was the German SS-- the local SS.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
